The paper focuses on automatic acquisition of commonsense knowledge, which is a core topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The methodology involves tapping into search-engine query logs and QA forums, which are natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR) tasks (cs.CL and cs.IR). The paper also mentions statistical cues and machine learning techniques, which fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with knowledge representation and reasoning, which is a sub-topic in computational complexity (cs.CY).
